sequenceDiagram
    participant MD as Market Data<br/>(MNQ 5-min Feed)
    participant MSE as Layer 1<br/>Market State Engine
    participant ADE as Layer 2<br/>Atlas Decision Engine
    participant A1 as Model A1<br/>Evaluator
    participant A3 as Model A3<br/>Evaluator
    participant B1 as Model B1<br/>Evaluator
    participant ARI as Layer 3<br/>Atlas Risk Intelligence
    participant EE as Layer 4<br/>Execution Engine
    participant TV as TradingView<br/>Pine Strategy
    participant WH as Webhook<br/>Receiver
    participant TP as TradersPost
    participant BR as Tradovate<br/>Broker
    participant OBS as Layer 5<br/>Observatory

    Note over MD,OBS: Every completed 5-minute candle triggers the full evaluation cycle

    MD->>MSE: Bar close (OHLCV + transactions)
    activate MSE
    MSE->>MSE: Compute 56-field Market State Object
    MSE->>MSE: Classify session, regime, MVC states
    MSE-->>OBS: MARKET_STATE_SNAPSHOT record
    MSE->>ADE: Market State Object (immutable)
    deactivate MSE

    activate ADE
    Note over ADE: Parallel independent evaluation
    ADE->>A1: Market State Object
    ADE->>A3: Market State Object
    ADE->>B1: Market State Object

    activate A1
    A1->>A1: Evaluate signal conditions
    A1->>A1: Compute Edge Score (7 components)
    A1-->>ADE: {eligible, edge_score, entry, stop, target}
    deactivate A1

    activate A3
    A3->>A3: Evaluate signal conditions
    A3->>A3: Compute Edge Score (7 components)
    A3-->>ADE: {eligible, edge_score, entry, stop, target}
    deactivate A3

    activate B1
    B1->>B1: Evaluate MVC-003 signal
    B1->>B1: Compute Edge Score (7 components)
    B1-->>ADE: {eligible, edge_score, entry, stop, target}
    deactivate B1

    ADE->>ADE: Rank eligible models by Edge Score
    ADE->>ADE: Select Candidate Model (highest score >= 60)
    ADE-->>OBS: ADE_EVALUATION record (all scores, selection)

    alt No model eligible (all scores < 60)
        ADE-->>OBS: NO_TRADE record
        Note over ADE: Atlas does not trade
    else Candidate Model selected
        ADE->>ARI: Candidate Model output
        deactivate ADE

        activate ARI
        ARI->>ARI: Check R1: Active position block
        ARI->>ARI: Check R2: Circuit breaker
        ARI->>ARI: Check R3: Daily loss limit
        ARI->>ARI: Check R4: Consecutive loss caution
        ARI->>ARI: Check R5: Daily trade limit
        ARI->>ARI: Check R6: Drawdown reduction
        ARI->>ARI: Check R7: Profit compounding
        ARI->>ARI: Check R8: Session end block
        ARI->>ARI: Calculate contracts & risk multiplier
        ARI-->>OBS: ARI_DECISION record

        alt ARI Rejects
            ARI-->>OBS: MISSED_OPPORTUNITY record
            Note over ARI: No execution
        else ARI Approves
            ARI->>EE: Approved trade (model, contracts, entry, stop, target)
            deactivate ARI

            activate EE
            EE->>TV: Signal parameters
            activate TV
            TV->>TV: Validate barstate.isrealtime
            TV->>TV: Generate alert JSON payload
            TV->>TV: Attach signal_id (duplicate prevention)
            TV->>WH: HTTP POST (webhook payload)
            deactivate TV

            activate WH
            WH->>WH: Validate payload schema
            WH->>WH: Check signal_id cache (duplicate prevention)
            WH->>WH: Verify position not already open
            WH->>TP: Validated trade instruction
            deactivate WH

            activate TP
            TP->>TP: Route to all configured accounts
            TP->>BR: Order (Prop Account 1)
            TP->>BR: Order (Prop Account 2)
            TP->>BR: Order (Live Account)
            deactivate TP

            activate BR
            BR->>BR: Execute market order
            BR-->>EE: Order confirmation + fill price
            deactivate BR

            EE-->>OBS: TRADE_ENTRY record
            deactivate EE

            Note over BR,OBS: Trade is now live — monitoring begins

            BR-->>EE: Stop hit / Target hit / Manual close
            activate EE
            EE->>ARI: Update ARI state (P&L, consecutive losses)
            EE-->>OBS: TRADE_EXIT record
            deactivate EE

            ARI->>ARI: Update consecutive_losses, daily_pnl, equity_peak
        end
    end

    OBS-->>OBS: Retain immutable record
    Note over OBS: Read-only — never modifies production behaviour
